	Waterox
	start
	20 G=(parm(3)- m*55.845)#gFe ASSUMING ONLY WATER CONSUMES IRON
	21 if G<0 then G=0
	22 IAP = ACT("Fe+2")*ACT("H2")*ACT("OH-")*ACT("OH-")
	23 if ((IAP/parm(2))-1)<0 then rate = parm(1)*G*((IAP/parm(2))-1) else rate=0
	80 moles=rate*time
	200 save moles
	end
